data.description: Welcome to the exquisite, gated community of Breckenridge. This captivating home is situated on a 1/4 acre lot and offers 4-bedrooms and 2-bathrooms with an abundance of space, luxurious features, and a location that's simply hard to beat. Nestled in the heart of Apopka, this residence boasts a charming neighborhood with a community pool and is within close proximity to parks, shops, and major roadways, making it the ideal place to call home. With three generously sized bedrooms and two elegantly appointed bathrooms, this home provides ample space for comfortable living. The extra den offers versatility, whether it's for a home office, study, or playroom. The gourmet kitchen is a culinary delight, equipped with a double oven, flat top range, built-in microwave, wine rack, center island, 42" cabinets, and a pantry closet. The breakfast bar is perfect for casual dining. The formal dining room is designed for entertaining and creating lasting memories with loved ones. Brand new carpets throughout and rich hardwood floors in the dining room and foyer add a touch of elegance and warmth to the living spaces. The spacious master bedroom features two walk-in closets for all your storage needs, while the master bathroom boasts dual sinks, a garden tub, and a separate shower for a spa-like experience. Enjoy the Florida sunshine in your private, fenced backyard, perfect for outdoor gatherings and gardening. The three-car garage, located to the side of the house, provides ample space for your vehicles and storage. As a resident, you'll have access to the community pool, a wonderful place to relax and cool off on hot summer days. This impeccable property is the epitome of comfortable living, combining spacious interiors, upscale features, and a fantastic location. Don't miss this opportunity to make it your own. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and discover the lifestyle that awaits you in Apopka, FL.  Matterport video available in listing.
